```mermaid
graph TD
    Client[Web Browser Client]

    subgraph Massive Monolithic Application Server
        UI[Presentation Layer]
        Auth[Authentication Package]
        Inventory[Inventory Management Package]
        Billing[Billing & Payment Package]
        Shipping[Shipping Logistics Package]
        
        UI <--> Auth
        UI <--> Inventory
        UI <--> Billing
        Inventory <--> Billing
        Inventory <--> Shipping
        Billing <--> Shipping
        Auth <--> Shipping
    end

    subgraph Single Relational Database
        DB[(Enterprise Database)]
    end

    Client <--> UI
    Auth <--> DB
    Inventory <--> DB
    Billing <--> DB
    Shipping <--> DB

    classDef danger fill:#ffcccc,stroke:#ff0000,stroke-width:2px;
    class Billing danger
    class DB danger
```
